Description: Preparations of cereals, flour, starch or milk; bakers' wares

Subentries.Description: Prepared foods obtained by the swelling or roasting of cereals or cereal products (for example, cornflakes); cereals (other than corn (maize)) in grain form or in the form of flakes or other worked grains (except flour, groats and meal), pre-cooked or otherwise prepared, not elsewhere specified or included:
Prepared foods obtained by the swelling or roasting of cereals or cereal products
